Class LongStack

Accountable, LongCollection, LongContainer, LongIndexedContainer, Preallocable, Cloneable, Iterable<LongCursor>, RandomAccess
@Generated(date="2021-12-15T09:58:17+0100", value="KTypeStack.java") public class LongStack extends LongArrayList
A subclass of LongArrayList adding stack-related utility methods. The top of the stack is at the LongArrayList.size() - 1 element.
